videos.headline: Boise State gets tricky
videos.description: Facing off against its former coach, the Broncos pulled off a WR pass from Thomas Sperbeck to Holden Huff, who made a diving catch for a 23-yard gain.

videos.headline: Washington returns punt for 76-yard TD
videos.description: With the help of some huge blocks, Dante Pettis sped down the sideline to pull Washington within a score. Boise State leads 16-10 at the end of the third quarter.
